I know in cities, and I think
this is more true in New York,

00:47:38.460 --> 00:47:40.660
people don't go out because
their houses are too small.

00:47:40.660 --> 00:47:41.760
But people don't cook at home.

00:47:41.760 --> 00:47:42.885
Their houses are too small.

00:47:42.885 --> 00:47:43.940
Everyone's going out.

00:47:43.940 --> 00:47:45.730
And in San Francisco,
people go out a lot.

00:47:45.730 --> 00:47:47.438
There are a lot of
wonderful restaurants,

00:47:47.438 --> 00:47:49.190
and it's fun to
meet friends out.

00:47:49.190 --> 00:47:52.330
But it's also really fun
to cook together at home.

00:47:52.330 --> 00:47:53.580
In most cases, it's healthier.

00:47:53.580 --> 00:47:55.850
In most cases, it'll
save you money.

00:47:55.850 --> 00:47:57.580
In most cases, you'll
have more fun too.

